<a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ADnh-L%C3%A2n/Ng%E1%BB%A5c-trung-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%C3%A2u-Dung/poem-XMGdymSO2vJrzNkAXg3zmQ">Ngục trung tặng Trâu Dung - 獄中贈鄒容</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ADnh-L%C3%A2n/author-xa5wRcmec3X_CkiNBflc8g">Chương Bính Lân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%E1%BB%AF-B%E1%BA%ADt/Quan-Chu-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%C3%BA/poem-t5SDq6ooOoPLPyHT8hFmCg">Quan Chu nhạc phú - 觀周樂賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%E1%BB%AF-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-TDh6Z0N6kQIoYYwYA3fCGw">Nguyễn Nhữ Bật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0-T%C4%A9nh/Qu%E1%BA%BF-Nguy%C3%AAn-t%E1%BA%A3o-h%C3%A0nh/poem-EadbrTTR0L0AJYzHHuaaJg">Quế Nguyên tảo hành - 桂源早行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0-T%C4%A9nh/author-IZjj0y8pXH2yUoEfzyz79Q">Dư Tĩnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Hu%E1%BB%91ng/Tu%E1%BA%BF-nh%E1%BA%ADt-t%C3%A1c/poem-fAdyQFJ9AD2Oh_H6V_kd9w">Tuế nhật tác - 歲日作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Hu%E1%BB%91ng/author-s27cAGHwrATcau0Gm-2RLQ">Cố Huống</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
